%% Diagram: Cache-priority Service Worker strategies (cache-first, cache-only)
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    CF1["Cache-First: fetch"] --> CF2{cached?}
    CF2 -->|hit| CF3[return cached]
    CF2 -->|miss| CF4[network + cache + return]
    CF3 ~~~ CO1
    CF4 ~~~ CO1
    CO1["Cache-Only: fetch"] --> CO2{cached?}
    CO2 -->|hit| CO3[return cached]
    CO2 -->|miss| CO4[offline page]
